TempratuurText: I-sensor yokushisa inikeza izilinganiso ezichanekileyo zezinga lokushisa lamanzi. Lokhu kubalulekile ngoba izinga lokushisa linethonya elikhulu ezinqubweni ze-biological kanye nasekuphuculeni umkhiqizo wamanzi. I-sensor inikeza izilinganiso ezisheshayo nezithembekile, ezinconyelwe ukumisa imvelo ngezikhathi zangempela kanye nokuhlaziywa kwezinguquko zoshisa.
PhSensorText: I-sensor ye-pH ilinganisa izinga le-acidity lamanzi ngokuhlaziya inani lama-ion e-hydrogen (H+). Lokhu kubalulekile ekutholeni izinguquko kumkhakha we-chemical balance kanye nokuthola ukungcola okungenzeka. Ngokunemba nangokushesha, i-sensor isekela ukuphathwa kwezakhiwo zamanzi eziphilayo.
TroebelheidText: I-sensor ye-oxygen ilinganisa isamba se-oxygen esixubile emanzini, okuyinto ebalulekile empilweni yokuhlala kwezilwane zamanzi. I-sensor inikeza idatha yesikhathi sangempela yokulawula amazinga e-oxygen, okuvumela ukugxila kuzinkinga ngokushesha.
ZuurstofText: I-sensor ye-turbidity ihlola ukukhanya kwamanzi ngokulinganisa ubungako bokukhanya obudlula emanzini. Lokhu kusiza ekutholeni ukungcola noma amaqembu emanzini, okuyinto ebaluleke kakhulu ekuhloleni umphumela wamanzi.
